data.description: MOVE IN FEB/MARCH 2022! HOME TO BE BUILT. At Patriots Walke's The Robert Frost is the home you've been searching for. This comfortable home offers 3 Bedrooms and 2 Baths upstairs, including large Owner's Suite and oversized WIC. Downstairs you have an open floor plan complete with Kitchen, Family Room, formal Dining Room, and a half Bath. Other features include LVP flooring, granite kitchen countertops, a full front porch, NEST digital thermostat, and so much more! What's that? It's The Robert Frost calling your name! Unbeatable pricing & location. Also, take advantage of the beautiful weather in the communities' large 2 acre park and picnic area. The only Homesite offering THIS floor plan. CALL NOW TO SCHEDULE YOUR APPOINTMENT!
